Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part A ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,低轨道机动战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,演变成集体突入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,凭借G-Self的高性能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于见到圭亚那高原的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,矗立在大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,开着这种高性能机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,远古巨兽号呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家是怎么突破大气层的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,金星殖民圈的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,令人感动！ 贝鲁利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,击伤玛尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这笔帐必须清算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,玛尼退后！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self上空 还有两架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,刚出Dharma的Dahack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦归麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以Dharama为载机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,投送这架Dahack上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,熟练使用掠能器和四把光束军刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,才不辱天才之名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,米克 后方又来两架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,又来两架？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,中央的不明机体外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,各式G-IT团机体云集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dahack和Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,被弦月船顺手牵羊后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,变成敌人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,用它进行古典式大气层突破的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就会尝到奇亚队长钟爱的光束鞭挞的滋味！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不急着米诺夫斯基飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗空域…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,伊赛拉 为什么放她走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下要救贝鲁利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利有什么好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self+完美背包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达 减速慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是一号站点上出发的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital军的军舰和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚舰队威胁更大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚舰队已经全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,北面下方 圭亚那高原方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,机体转向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,北面下方的舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来 父亲频繁来回地球是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚想趁机占领Capital特区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个尼肯宁总统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,完全做得出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,光信号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Lucifer的光信号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,光信号下方 发现疑似舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拉特尔派森和鳄鱼级 四艘！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,尼肯宁总统到底浪费了多少税金…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,伊赛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一号站点出发的布鲁金在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,根据米诺夫斯基粒子的方向推测
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝这里降落！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对托瓦萨格出身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,兼Capital幕后黑手的昆帕上校来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不算什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,史堤厄 右舵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,右舷下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,显示地面图像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是支舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那种速成舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁金的Ousia部队足以应付
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉也在战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看起来想打陆战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,机动战士和宇宙舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想打陆战？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Rach的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,千足虫！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别以为块头大…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是宇宙返航的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Rach呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,远程监视器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队在贴地飞行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,两处接战？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是四处 好像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会有亚美利亚舰队？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,从没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,护罩 躲避光束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在三方混战 不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想死于别人家的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,冲破舰队进入加勒比海！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么喜欢混战？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人都是战争狂么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您说现在着陆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想近距离观察葛兰登号的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,玛尼和葛兰登号会合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样没法帮助卢因！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定也对当前情况感到困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,回到他出生的大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不认为是送他归天的好机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,跳级生到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,必须阻止舰队战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,将来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,成为独裁者的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,血统的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,从这世上消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,从这世上？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,限制行动？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,全方位激光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self是恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,玛尼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,功率不能持续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是金星殖民圈的机体强力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,卢因 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,米克对付上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,契卡拉 那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,米克 太鲁莽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这机体是他们造的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 因此也了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的战法和底牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可想而知金星殖民圈G-IT实验室的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那编队是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,集火目标葛兰登号的亚美利亚舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙是哪儿来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那舰队与面具为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这种场合来自下方的攻击最奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在去阻止亚美利亚舰队是送死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们停止执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲策划的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在朝南移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁的军舰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘军舰的上空！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,长官！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,难道贝鲁也在那战场上？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,台地底下的丛林里也有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,长官！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亚队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…Dahack！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,七杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 九杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第四架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Trinity和Dahack是亚美利亚一边的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,G-IT团只有一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知道那艘巨舰的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真面目？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘船上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就像个得到玩具的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是从下方攻击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那上面的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们根本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白使用它意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅 诺蕾朵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,完美背包虽然名不虚传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏这时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这么连续作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在地面爬行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,实在不适合你 跳级生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,杀不了你是昆达拉的耻辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,强袭模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,电池耗尽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利·塞纳姆同学！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part B ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,狡诈模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,凹陷的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就算没有米诺夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电也接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么金星殖民圈的G-IT团！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一群怀古主义的历史宅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早就看出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,诸位从金星殖民圈千里迢迢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,送上门来让我杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亚队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dahack的光束有这么强力？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dahack！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算无暇作为掠能器使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,也可作为护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,虚张声势！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,能量在被吸走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亚队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,契卡拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,敢在我面前东张西望！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米克战斗得足够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆的Dahack也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,左手已经不能用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,欺负米克的是黑色的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要收拾它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,米克会拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很想称赞古匈长官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,筹备舰队的先见之明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但还远未形成战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,远古巨兽和布鲁金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快告诉妈妈你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了 光子扫描器！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让能量高的地方安静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就能避免牺牲结束战争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self 光子扫描器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,获取数据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别下坠 跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,光子力最强的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让它无法使用就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还能坚持多久？ 跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,玛尼 葛兰登在更北面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利 为了卢因死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让G-Self逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,下面的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玛尼和葛兰登会合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别用浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,卢因学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什么忙也…帮不上！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙世纪时代的遗迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self的藏身处！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 刚才的跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看来电池已经耗尽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,胜负 在此一举！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只摧毁武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没…没辙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,脱出！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让你再装轰炸机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,林戈先生和凯尔贝斯教官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大气层滑翔机？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是贝鲁吗 贝鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这束缚是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么绑我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是绑 是连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和你的光束鞭不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明白意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是孩子 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,G吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟踪翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,枪口？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,雷哈顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还能行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存者营救遇难人员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital军的布鲁金也已经迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,营救所有遇难人员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,以亚美利亚的艾达·苏尔坎之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁 贝鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小心脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亚队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上也有那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好想 让你见见他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真能跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有一公里以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在托瓦萨格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也经常瞒着别人东奔西跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,连米拉基和洛卢卡先生也瞒着？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟身份接近间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下就能穿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看来时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,回托瓦萨格再考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,女人真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 这样模拟满月就设定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,OK 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只送到亚美利亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,按时发车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！他们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油 弦月船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油 弦月船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,世界巡游
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,终于开始环球之旅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,卢因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,玉米汤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,本次宇宙战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,献出生命的英勇将士们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为保卫祖国亚美利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,履行了他们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子克里姆顿·尼肯宁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也为国捐躯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}月亮裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,月…月亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:20:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}不是月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,用弦月船压死总统 史堤厄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别拦我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜利用自己孩子的战死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的总统死有余辜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,理解你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,托瓦萨格人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亚·穆贝二世？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不好听？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,米克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不…不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚下船了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在日本停过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,诺蕾朵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他要我转告你 啾啾咪就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是叫富士山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫它三峰富士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shank能爬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有山路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,下山走须走口15分钟就到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,原来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,背后是太平洋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,前方是日本海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,穿过海洋 进入大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用它环游世界！
